data.text:
7:00PM - 7:00PM

Drake 2060 (New Works Lab)

Pretty Girls Don’t Eat

a solo performance

by Kelly Hogan (BA Theatre Student)

Pretty Girls Don't Eatis a solo show created by Kelly Hogan, based on of her personal experience with eating disorders and warped self-perception in high school. It follows her struggle with starving, purging, and the dark mindset she lived in as a young teenager.

For mature audiences only.This performance may be triggering for those who have suffered or are suffering from eating disorders.

Monday and Tuesday, October 6 & 7

7 PM

Drake 2060, New Works Lab

Admission Free

Tickets first come, first served
